# SEO, Accessibility, and Performance Standards

SEO:
Every public page should include:
- Title
- Meta description
- Open Graph title
- Open Graph description
- Open Graph image where available
- Canonical URL where applicable

SEO themes:
- Custom menswear
- Custom shirts for men
- Tailored trousers
- Custom jeans
- Embroidered jeans for men
- Custom denim
- Weddingwear for men
- Groom outfits
- Statement menswear
- Personalized clothing for men
- Made-to-measure shirts
- Custom embroidered clothing

Accessibility:
- Use semantic HTML.
- Use proper heading order.
- Add alt text for meaningful images.
- Hide decorative images from screen readers.
- Use keyboard-accessible menus.
- Use visible focus states.
- Connect labels to inputs.
- Connect errors to fields.
- Do not rely on color alone for selected states.
- Respect reduced-motion preferences.

Performance:
- Optimize images.
- Use responsive images.
- Lazy-load below-the-fold media.
- Avoid heavy Instagram embeds above the fold.
- Avoid unnecessary client-side JavaScript.
- Avoid oversized animation libraries unless already used.
- Keep homepage fast on mobile.

A premium site must feel fast, not just look expensive.
